msgctxt "56_Man With a Past"
msgid "Hey, don't start doing anything shady, okay? Cops are everywhere, and I can't have them thinkin' I've got anything to do with you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68_Man With a Past"
msgid "The police in Kamurocho are on high alert. They have sent many of their officers out on patrol around the town to make sure they catch anyone acting suspicious."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80_Man With a Past"
msgid "There are two types of officers: some stand guard in place and watch their surroundings, while others follow a patrol and approach shady individuals to question them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92_Man With a Past"
msgid "Running down the street will attract the attention of patrolling officers.\\r\n"
"You may want to enter first-person mode with <Action:Button_R3@Adventure> and check for officers before moving quickly."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104_Man With a Past"
msgid "This information has been added as a <Color:14>memo<Color:Default>.\\r\n"
"Read <Color:14>memos<Color:Default> by selecting <Color:14>Memos<Color:Default> in the Pause Menu.\\r\n"
"You can access the Pause Menu with the <Action:Button_Options@Adventure> button."
msgstr ""

